r />\nJonathan Ng<br />\nActing Registrar<br />\nHong Kong Institute of Certified Public Accountants<br />\nDated this 29th day of December 2017<br />\n<br />\n去的請舉手"},{"pid":"dffac3681684d7e9bf2d004c6b96e40da71ad1b7","tid":567963,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"今晚可能6:00就要等搭lift上去"},{"pid":"fc4868607b9b1e95a1a35e179ed594d2128f9654","tid":567963,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"有冇人會去<br />\n而且可以現場直擊報導 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c105c50d540535b28d07a90c7cbd0b4a3f17a404","tid":567963,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T10:15:47.000Z","msg":"排緊隊上去"},{"pid":"ecd22ac8dbcc29d4e32c791dd60cc9d5fd2cce22","tid":567963,"uid":10460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"已上"},{"pid":"fea8708f71dc33693f921e9386984dc67c4a80f3","tid":567963,"uid":159234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T10:59:44.000Z","msg":"屌佢老尾  卒撚死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56dcf0393733b5aae86f2205c9ab717af2146c2","tid":567963,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:06:58.000Z","msg":"好多人仲未入到"},{"pid":"07051f84db7986390b9e061f58405690cce28298","tid":567963,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:07:15.000Z","msg":"樓下排長龍等lift"},{"pid":"12c704919a379c6bc8fa1958814bd1e315891591","tid":567963,"uid":24168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"好長龍..."},{"pid":"727680b634da6185759